後有四個消防的走左佢，不知下落。該男性穿非黑衫。<br />\n<br />\n教大學生會會長:一名市民呼吸困難，最後暈低，警察叫佢唔好訓，拖埋佢一邊，好耐都冇救護員，有消防員出現過但不知帶了去哪裡，完成拘留後出來都冇見過佢。<br />\n<br />\n該男性穿街坊裝，非黑衫，冇gear係身。佢暈低不適時其他市民都已經叫警員找救護員救護車，警方冇理會到，只係自行所謂協助。該男士非毛ee圖中那幾位。<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n公開cctv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef61e46ffb968811551ddf45167738d4f881fc1","tid":1554801,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77374a87f05b916aff34ab0a5c554e3e721c022d","tid":1554801,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"屌 有人偷月餅又可以睇片"},{"pid":"c6d401fbd93536ae6605ac6132fde7cb23c96a8c","tid":1554801,"uid":53029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"，，，，"},{"pid":"86fc6d5d6b6c48d6ae2a4ea9fc601c98b3548891","tid":1554801,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6868be6f9ab2121a2b68a60d004a09f53bdadcfb","tid":1554801,"uid":276464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"身有屎就身有屎啦 你老母 私隱 打格仔咪得囉"},{"pid":"2cddd23f7aa9d74cc63ca66d26fc1c723fc1b54d","tid":1554801,"uid":99478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"double standard."},{"pid":"cf928d9821ba0e23c993f2602eb1a9792088c0f6","tid":1554801,"uid":101383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e6579399cb6ef6ea6f25d7a9dffa71d7d836fe8","tid":1554801,"uid":119352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b50111bdb433789366a448d27a0e29b29a2bad","tid":1554801,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】運輸及房屋局局長陳帆及港鐵高層視察受破壞的港鐵站。港鐵指，正和政府部門研究能否公開831太子站的閉路電視片段，但由於涉及其他市民的資料，需慎重考慮。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成：「閉路電視內的記錄很多牽涉其他人的資料，大家放心，我知道大家的關注，所以在這方面都要思考好，但大家最近的關心不需關心、擔心，因為我們的記錄一定會保留起碼三年，這方面大家可繼續討論。」<br />\n<br />\n陳帆：「香港鐵路是香港人的鐵路，很重要的是，它每天服務五百四十萬人，是香港公共交通重要的持份者。損壞鐵路設施，即是損壞香港市民享用有效率的公共服務。我希望參與破壞設施的暴亂人士尊重香港人出行的自由和權利。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗又公佈得？而家你肯公開都未必有人信啦我屌你老母，就算無人死班狗都一定醜態百出</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"三年又三年"},{"pid":"805fcf37ac660a0e1064050782d7c7fa9d9637b4","tid":1554801,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"成個星期喇，又封咗幾晚站，仲未拍好？"},{"pid":"38128d2c5273c61e49d1f3bbc01a0fadfc167cd6","tid":1554801,"uid":306692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f24999d26efe57e2fcabd7f7a98e120ef133c1","tid":1554801,"uid":109890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a35e77956a4f9acf23dcfafafe5a1e3b3ca20ae","tid":1554801,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"cbbbb9d44e08c54afd50c79f727377131b5d7a92","tid":1554801,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil