me":"2019-09-09T07:38:33.000Z","msg":"堅嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760811178d0b4fd2cda062dba5644c9b8576c069","tid":1554801,"uid":118176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a536f16fbd0b8e870ec37459b5db5410aa74ce9a","tid":1554801,"uid":224646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78b50111bdb433789366a448d27a0e29b29a2bad","tid":1554801,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】運輸及房屋局局長陳帆及港鐵高層視察受破壞的港鐵站。港鐵指，正和政府部門研究能否公開831太子站的閉路電視片段，但由於涉及其他市民的資料，需慎重考慮。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成：「閉路電視內的記錄很多牽涉其他人的資料，大家放心，我知道大家的關注，所以在這方面都要思考好，但大家最近的關心不需關心、擔心，因為我們的記錄一定會保留起碼三年，這方面大家可繼續討論。」<br />\n<br />\n陳帆：「香港鐵路是香港人的鐵路，很重要的是，它每天服務五百四十萬人，是香港公共交通重要的持份者。損壞鐵路設施，即是損壞香港市民享用有效率的公共服務。我希望參與破壞設施的暴亂人士尊重香港人出行的自由和權利。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗又公佈得？而家你肯公開都未必有人信啦我屌你老母，就算無人死班狗都一定醜態百出</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"手動轉【白宮聯署 - 更新 09.09.2019 】<br />\n當我知道尋晚「最喜愛香港小姐」嘅投票數係 176 萬，我有啲想喊。<br />\n<br />\n1/ 每個聯署簽一個好嘞。簽完記得MARK返自己簽過。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽署＞等電郵＞確認簽署＞叫十個朋友簽<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民（最後兩天）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsend-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=672a526c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/send-military-force-hong-kong-save-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-beginning-11-aug</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政府及警察策動831太子恐怖襲擊，請美國予以制裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=5ba112ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-conducted-prince-edward-train-station-hong-kong-831</a><br />\n-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests"},{"pid":"e336815829015632e1af0e115181cf4dd1660635","tid":1554801,"uid":229872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8beee10e9e4e544100eeb1b1971c5b73308dd79","tid":1554801,"uid":125168,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"改完片未？遮樣公佈cctv係咪咁簡單都唔識？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"等緊完左國慶先敢放。"},{"pid":"bdf2b76f0d9c4f51d2f47fed348eb407b1a86c67","tid":1554801,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />龍門任佢搬"},{"pid":"1c9f1dfa70e4cae58c96a3eae3790353cae09dd9","tid":1554801,"uid":112001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4966760f2380780f34c3e7156bace7e77971e48c","tid":1554801,"uid":41818,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"做假都要時間，等等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"每晚得幾個鐘拍片 大家俾啲時間"},{"pid":"7c8942d3d14706670357ebd26c31157cecd0f277","tid":1554801,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"比狗果陣又咁快手<br />\n而家公開就話要慎重考慮"},{"pid":"c78ed1ee390aaac1e5b0b6d777542e3e41a4f5c3","tid":1554801,"uid":39547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:59:51.000Z","msg